Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:56.76,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Even though it's easy to say "I love you"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:59.98,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}when you stand in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:06.12,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}my personality stands up and gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:10.91,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I can usually pull through with my assertiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:14.46,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}that's just how I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:20.67,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}But no matter how hard I try, I can't break the wall that's between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:24.18,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I want you to realise… my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:27.80,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}So I always send a gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:31.72,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}of "I really love you" your way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:34.85,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}with all of my courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:39.00,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}My flimsy silky heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:42.32,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}After meeting you, I finally realised
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:47.92,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}that I'm really clumsy when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:53.19,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}The scars from love that I'd almost forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:56.75,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}have started to ache all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:02:00.34,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Someday, like how I normally would...
