Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:32.04,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}extended its roots
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:39.90,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}and put out a fruit that was still unripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:44.60,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The fruit that I wish would turn orange soon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:47.68,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}is bathed in your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:51.42,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The ideals and dreams just swell{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:54.33,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\fnGill Sans Std ExtraBold Display\b1\c&HBDCACF&}H{\r}ey, feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:58.27,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Today, I tried eating an orange
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:01.52,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}but it was so sour I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:04.99,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I couldn’t leave it behind like I have been
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.99,0:23:07.57,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}so I ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:13.69,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it… I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:20.83,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it… I love it.
