Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't that serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should go and visit him later{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up sleeping through the whole winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I face her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was... rejected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why did you close it again all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The noodles are soggy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating junk food again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're so annoying, I'll eat it right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've cooked for you every single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you come over since New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get mad at me just because Minorin rejected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I want you to pity me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just treat me like you usually do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this for the sake of you and Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd support Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I always just crash at your place.{TLC please, doesn't seem right in the context - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for her to misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you think that's why she rejected me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she just doesn't feel that w{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think Minorin likes you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she probably thinks I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think Minorin doesn't like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling she's kind of interested in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't come over anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to wake me up every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still feel the same about Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll change her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you should do what you should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away from Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to confirm her true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't burn down your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I promise I won't use the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby declare that I'll only eat fast food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, I wonder how long you'll last.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll last, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:04:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, you forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even stamped it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stamped?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Okinawa thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're really going to Okinawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for me to care about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see Kushieda, the first thing I'll do is greet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to return this to you as soon as\Npossible since it looked really expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I traded you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this was in the pocket the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't end up needing it that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea! The sun! Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Herbal wine! Chinsuko! Okinawa!{add TL note? : Chinsuko is a traditional biscuit sweet often sold as a souvenir in Okinawa}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six days and five nights in Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Taka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga! Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Penis...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga's going to bite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were bothering me with your chinsuko crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it look on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is still Ryuuji's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.97,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you guys are all hyped up for the new semester!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-G{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish everything would just burn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It burned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the field trip won't be cancelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go as planned, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I don't understand what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel we were going to stay at in Okinawa burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The field trip will now be a ski trip for three days and two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I burned the hotel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Objection! This is nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Ami-chan late on a day like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ami-chan were here, she'd definitely have a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima-san was modelling in Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't make it back for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since she's already spent a lot of time in the southern islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd probably want to go to a snowy mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Taiga said she had something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll try my best by myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you still feel the same about Minorin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's even living on cup noodles for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be working in Hawaii?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be picking a fight when we haven't even seen each other recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you because you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to meet ten minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so picky, Stupid Chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is what you were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys are already friendly enough to exchange gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I paid for it, so it's not actually a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is useless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just wear it when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to take it with you to Okinawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The field trip is now a ski trip for three days and two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said the hotel in Okinawa burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologising?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you before the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, don't hang around Ryuuji during the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd bother {\i1}me{\i0} to hang around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Ryuuji was rejected by Minorin on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it was right before I was going to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She rejected me by hinting that I shouldn't confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Minorin really likes Ryuuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for some reason, things aren't moving along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have exams once we're seniors, and we'll be in different classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This field trip is his last chance to confirm Minorin's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that, Stupid Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with it if you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a boring conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully you're the {\i1}only{\i0} one getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as stupid as you could never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you following me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd go that far for Kushieda and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, so... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:12:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best on the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps confirming Kushieda's feelings would be a waste of effort, but{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Minorin like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where did you get all that confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reason to believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're capable of becoming Minori's lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm going to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a new convenience store there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with that attitude today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't move forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't even on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm going first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take care of this since you got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Taiga, damn that Taiga, damn that{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.07,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm totally all right with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let me hold a side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, your hair looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cut the front a bit shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I wanted to cut it so short that even berries could grow on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like a guy's hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always had a buzz cut when I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would just sit at the barber's with my younger brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they'd just rip my hair off with clippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nickname back then was "Mr. Lady".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you noticed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because I always look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a shocking confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I have to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, your brother plays high school baseball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, his school frequently visits Koshien.{Add TL note: Koshien refers to Hanshin Koshien Stadium near Kobe in Japan, which holds the national high school baseball tournaments - ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'd be proud of him if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm a bit jealous of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-senpai, Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really "oh my".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "oh my"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the groups for the field trip are decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this grouping is really weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Ami, Kashii, Aisaka, Kushieda, Takasu, Noto, Haruta, and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mixture of nine boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have more girls, I think this is a good grouping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you and Taiga will be{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! But if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not happy about it, go join another group.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying, so I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:16:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you tell me to shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.20,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to, you can go join{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that's not the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, even Master Kitamura said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buzz off, Noto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to say such things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to make a guidebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, each group needs to turn it in by next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to do something so troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be easier if we worked together on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about my place on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my place is pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't this place a bit over the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much the rent is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, do you live next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you live in this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live in an apartment next to this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a few examples from previous field trips for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are guides inside these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of a master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make some black tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also brought some madeleines over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka, I need to use the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the outlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's behind the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you can talk to Kitamura normally now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't really care about it, just go and help Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Golgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Golgo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'm Golgo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird that there's usable tableware in Taiga's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time I came here was during our freshman year,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't been doing anything lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga did this all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason she's able to do it is because you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been here since freshman year?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because of the stuff with her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I wouldn't come here unless I had a reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of failing, so I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you did a good job, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't afraid of failing, and you stepped in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it'd be all right if we just copied this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would we copy an Okinawa guide\Nwhen we're going to a snowy mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, we can't show Yuusaku this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.66,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you should worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just making me more curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I guess it must be a big shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a picture, but that magnificent rejection{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid Chi'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:09.01,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Blame the person who brought this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, tea's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, be nice to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.81,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, I'm kind of looking forward to this field trip.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I mean, it's the last time our class will be doing something together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This class is really fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be lonely without it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only we could stay like this forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, you're right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only we could stay like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...staying like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually sorted them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I can't stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to confirm Kushieda's true feelings on the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ni-Ni-Ni... Nigauri (Bitter melon).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-Ri-Ri... Richiumu Denchi (Lithium battery).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chinome (Blood blister).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meidosan no hesonogoma (A maid's belly button fluff).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mandoragora no benishuuga (Mandrake red pickled ginger).
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, start with "ga."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ganbaru (Do your best)!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The subject is bitter things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, wasted effort is "bitter" in a sense, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, start with "ru."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ru ru ru rurururu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.48,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Sukyatto suru Nigamigawa Shibuhiko\N(Scat-singing Nigamigawa Shibuhiko)!
